<div id="u-credit-00218-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jdque" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6406351); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6406351&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224347" alt="jdque" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6406351)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jdque" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6406351); return false;">jdque</a></span></p>
