<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00502/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一副AKG N50██耳机，在蓝牙模式开启后会随机选择一台半径10米之内的具有音频输出功能的电子设备（如手机，电脑等）并同步播放该设备上正在播放的音频<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>2020/12/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>由研究员Kimura L购买自京█，已确认同批次其它产品无异常性质<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>存放于Site-CN-19的低价值异常物品存放点，将其列装MTF-█████-█作为监听设备的请求待批准<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong> &quot;我明明把所有隐身窗口都关掉了&#8230;&#8230;&quot; &#8212;研究员Kimura L</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00502" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00502" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00502-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chengdu-hunters" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4982782); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4982782&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224347" alt="Chengdu Hunters" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4982782)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chengdu-hunters" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4982782); return false;">Chengdu Hunters</a></span></p>
